title: 11/19/20 HOUR 2- Nick Friedell
itunes:title: 11/19/20 HOUR 2- Nick Friedell
description:
Nick Friedell gives Dan and update from the Golden State Warriors camp as it pertains to Klay Thompson. Nick said that the team was still holding to hope that the injury was not as severe as first reported.
